.SH NAME
.PP
git smf
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
git smf command - iterate over submodules to execute shell command
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
git smf is a helper alias to execute shell commands in each submodule.
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP \[bu] 2
git smf pwd
.IP \[bu] 2
git smf \[lq]touch .gitignore\[rq]
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
